{
  "texts": [
    "We use the intra-category multi-tool subset (G3 split) of ToolBench as the seed dataset because it is the largest public tool usage dataset and requires the combined use of multiple tools from different categories to complete complex tasks.",
    "Each seed task contains an instruction and a solution tree, where the rightmost path of the tree is the seed solution.",
    "We removed seed tasks with invalid",
